ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of PAUL ANTHONY SUMMERVILLE of Victoria, British Columbia, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Mark Dwor, whose term has expired.
